{"tid":455114,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"你擇我譯 中英","createTime":"2017-11-01T20:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T07:43:09.000Z","uid":28257,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"eef5ee8281577a90ca535ef5ac7d0f1b5996147c","tid":455114,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T20:13:50.000Z","msg":"巴打好﹐我想練習一下寫野的文筆。奈可自己毅力唔夠，三分鐘熱度，放棄多過食飯。<br />\n<br />\n如果你有興趣，可以留低一段或一篇章的文字，或書名。我會試翻譯出黎。中只英或英至中都可以。希望，借此自己可以持之而恆。"},{"pid":"46071d80bb1a0bdb482a146b31a546cf7409c9a2","tid":455114,"uid":143151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T20:29:05.000Z","msg":"小王子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21bab74f3e406c677187adc6f5279463393ed39c","tid":455114,"uid":69021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T20:31:57.000Z","msg":"我個名"},{"pid":"ff0253cd3db9e486e9bbd175bd99b926517c2828","tid":455114,"uid":10608,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T23:04:03.000Z","msg":"寫依個<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://images.cqwin.com/upfile/newsfile/car/2014/09/52636190-b17a-476d-8c1f-ec8fec026e86.jpg[/img\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.cqwin.com%2Fupfile%2Fnewsfile%2Fcar%2F2014%2F09%2F52636190-b17a-476d-8c1f-ec8fec026e86.jpg%5B%2Fimg&d=GbBtzLsxIR2uf64XFZ3b3f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d5b777a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://images.cqwin.com/upfile/newsfile/car/2014/09/52636190-b17a-476d-8c1f-ec8fec026e86.jpg[/img</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">個人簽名</span><br />\n_______________________________________________________<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.cqwin.com/upfile/newsfile/car/2014/09/52636190-b17a-476d-8c1f-ec8fec026e86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.cqwin.com%2Fupfile%2Fnewsfile%2Fcar%2F2014%2F09%2F52636190-b17a-476d-8c1f-ec8fec026e86.jpg&h=9a7bf78e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74e26affb7fda2cec6cf591d03a1260