e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nso mk though<br />\n<br />\nSelfishly, I love you<br />\nSolely, wanted I to have you"},{"pid":"107fca2a0e6c60e1487fdf3d802d8d2545ca4dc7","tid":455114,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T23:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫依個<br />\n[img][url]<a href=\"http://images.cqwin.com/upfile/newsfile/car/2014/09/52636190-b17a-476d-8c1f-ec8fec026e86.jpg[/img[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.cqwin.com%2Fupfile%2Fnewsfile%2Fcar%2F2014%2F09%2F52636190-b17a-476d-8c1f-ec8fec026e86.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5B%2Furl%5D&d=GbBtzLsxIR2uf64XFZ3b3f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=148a4b25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://images.cqwin.com/upfile/newsfile/car/2014/09/52636190-b17a-476d-8c1f-ec8fec026e86.jpg[/img[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">個人簽名</span><br />\n_______________________________________________________<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.cqwin.com/upfile/newsfile/car/2014/09/52636190-b17a-476d-8c1f-ec8fec026e86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.cqwin.com%2Fupfile%2Fnewsfile%2Fcar%2F2014%2F09%2F52636190-b17a-476d-8c1f-ec8fec026e86.jpg&h=9a7bf78e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSelfishness out of loving you, out of wanting to have you"},{"pid":"8678928fba375d7e1e2c7b9f775e59b0af2cd5d4","tid":455114,"uid":28257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T23:49:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSex John Amballess"},{"pid":"fe3c72dbf691985f2ed4da639c4f747e4984f77c","tid":455114,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T23:50:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSex John Amballess</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSt John Amballess"},{"pid":"29293e68db4c71f42d9f49641d49614abfa8d52d","tid":455114,"uid":155005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T23:53:20.000Z","msg":"my name"},{"pid":"ae0a1c5b03fc2d3c7152341ec89eeda8d795727f","tid":455114,"uid":70205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T23:54:10.000Z","msg":"莫笑農家臘酒渾，豐年留客足雞豚。山重水複疑無路，柳暗花明又一村"},{"pid":"75adae579180652a782e0712f68a5e366a1488f3","tid":455114,"uid":124930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T23:55:22.000Z","msg":"床前明月光 疑是地上霜<br />\n舉頭望明月 低頭思故鄉"},{"pid":"62453271e1e808a56da627727d0b631485f54409","tid":455114,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T01:42:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>莫笑農家臘酒渾，豐年留客足雞豚。山重水複疑無路，柳暗花明又一村</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinesepoetryinenglishverse.blogspot.com/2013/09/hill-after-hill-rill-after-rill-it.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchinesepoetryinenglishverse.blogspot.com%2F2013%2F09%2Fhill-after-hill-rill-after-rill-it.html&d=GbBtzLsxIR2uf64XFZ3b3f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=921bb353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://chinesepoetryinenglishverse.blogspot.com/2013/09/hill-after-hill-rill-after-rill-it.html</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Touring the Village West of the Mountain&quot;  <br />\nTranslated by Frank C Yue <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLaugh not at the peasants' turbid, un-strained home-brew'd New Year wine;<br />\nThey'd slaughter chickens and pig for their guest when they have harvests fine.<br />\nHill after hill, rill after rill -- it seems the path leads to                 nowhere;<br />\nBeyond the shady willows, bright flow'rs, another village           lies there.<br />\n<br />\n詩係翻譯的終極大佬，要譯詩必先懂作詩，自問有心冇力。"},{"pid":"741856fb2a9e3515cc2b4f5dcb164365dc50d239","tid":455114,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T01:44:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>床前明月光 疑是地上霜<br />\n舉頭望明月 低頭思故鄉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n床前明月光<br />\n疑是地上霜<br />\n<br />\nBright moonlight before my bed;<br />\nI suppose it is frost on the ground.<br />\n<br />\n舉頭望明月<br />\n低頭思故鄉<br />\n<br />\nI raise my head to view the bright moon,<br />\nthen lower it, thinking of my home village.<br />\n<br />\nTranslated by Hugh Grigg<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://eastasiastudent.net/china/classical/li-bai-night-thoughts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastasiastudent.net%2Fchina%2Fclassical%2Fli-bai-night-thoughts%2F&d=GbBtzLsxIR2uf64XFZ3b3f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=bc4eb0b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eastasiastudent.net/china/classical/li-bai-night-thoughts/</a>"},{"pid":"f2fbf3eb3fac0bebcbddd46993370c310ce00c14","tid":455114,"uid":120202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T01:48:31.000Z","msg":"靚仔冇本心"},{"pid":"b4d732840cc890254d767b4962337e57821875dd","tid":455114,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T01:50:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"042f047ef69e3c05989d86edf5595191d9d6b05d","tid":455114,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:08:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>my name</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭髮未染霜　著涼亦錯在我幼稚<br />\n<br />\nHair yet to be frosted; my own naivety caught me a cold"},{"pid":"7d784d94eb6b7b625833f51d3724543533096b2f","tid":455114,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靚仔冇本心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCute guy is no keeper"},{"pid":"9554b007d298a5f4620dc8c101e287dddba54e8e","tid":455114,"uid":76931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:20:57.000Z","msg":"道可道 非常道"},{"pid":"c8029c65fd5785e176b8d357d454e26aff951cfd","tid":455114,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:27:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>道可道 非常道</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nA path, explicable, is not the absolute path"},{"pid":"e08f6125b168a3fe3bad4fef6bcd0dc2ee184d8f","tid":455114,"uid":22384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:34:21.000Z","msg":"My name<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcef0c56721c97a8f583cf00f5e446c9d9dbb21e","tid":455114,"uid":69581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:46:28.000Z","msg":"人在江湖，身不由己<br />\n<br />\n有緣無份<br />\n<br />\n一切有為法，如夢幻泡影，如露亦如電，應作如是觀<br />\n<br />\nTo be or not to be"}]}